Titolo: Cowboy Bebop: Tsuioku no Serenade

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Cowboy Bebop: Tsuioku no Serenade (カウボーイビバップ 追憶の夜曲（セレナーデ）, Kaubōi Bibappu: Tsuioku no Serenāde, lit. "Cowboy Bebop: Serenade of Reminiscence") is a PlayStation 2 action/beat 'em up video game from Bandai, released in Japan on August 25, 2005. It has an original story based on the anime series Cowboy Bebop.